-- Prudential Financial Promotes Parker to President of Investments
-- B y   A n d r e a   L u d t k e
-- 2012-01-17T19:35:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-17/prudential-financial-promotes-parker-to-president-of-investments.html
Prudential Financial Inc. (PRU) , the
second-largest U.S. life insurer, named Stuart Parker as
president of the mutual-fund and wealth-management business,
replacing Judy Rice.  Rice will be chairman of Prudential Investments until her
retirement at the end of this year, the  Newark , New Jersey-based
insurer said today in a statement distributed by  Business Wire .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrea Ludtke in New York at 
 aludtke@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  